&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Deal Cycle Management:&lt;/strong&gt; Proactively identify and target potential customers while managing a high volume of medium-complexity sales cycles simultaneously, including prospecting, discovery, demo, and closing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pipeline Management:&lt;/strong&gt; Build and manage a robust sales pipeline with multiple channels (AE self-generated, SDR, Events Marketing, and Inbound), ensuring a steady flow of qualified leads and opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Value Selling:&lt;/strong&gt; Position yourself as a &lt;strong&gt;trusted business advisor&lt;/strong&gt;, effectively articulating Brex’s unique value proposition and solving customer pain points by focusing on business outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Process-Driven Selling:&lt;/strong&gt; Follow established sales processes, including leveraging Solution Consultants (SCs), pulling vendor files, and utilizing Mutual Action

